        "Description": "In the depths of the ocean, Parkkonen lived inside a cozy banana, nestled between coral reefs. His days were full of fruity fun, sliding down the banana peel and playing with sea critters. The banana&apos;s golden glow lit up the underwater world, making Parkkonen&apos;s home the brightest spot in Bikini Bottom. Every day was a splash of sweetness, and Parkkonen loved his quirky, tropical life, proving that even under the sea, life can be a-peeling!",
